subject: Golf
lead_paragraph: Yani Tseng, a 19-year-old from Taiwan, finished a course-record eight-under-par 64 to complete the rain-delayed second round, then shot a 68 in the third to take a four-stroke lead over Se Re Pak in the Canadian Women’s Open in Ottawa. She had a 14-under 202 total.
